Hey Harry, Good news - I was just resetting some of the goal setups in Analytics and was able to find some numbers for this PDF download. Clicks from the RR Website for this year:
  • January - 12
  • February - 15
  • March - 10
  • April - 6
  • May - 5
  • June - 9
  • July - 16
  • August - 13
  • September - 13
  • October - 21
  • November - 4
I have also set up a goal in Google Analytics for this particular download to make it easier to find in future (this will pull in new data but not old data). As we migrate tracking over to GA4 I'll be mindful that you're tracking this and ensure this is set up correctly. More than happy to leave it on Dropbox, as it's close to 100MB, so I wouldn't suggest having this on your own server to avoid any performance issues. Just something to be mindful of is that if the link to this document changes, the tracking will also need to.
